    "h1": "TinyMCE – The Most Trusted & Feature-rich WYSIWYG Rich Text Editor",
    "h1_count": 1,
    "blockquote": "TinyMCE is an advanced WYSIWYG Rich Text Editor trusted by over 1.5M+ developers worldwide, with a platform that combines AI-powered tools, seamless integrations, and extensive customization for a superior rich text editing experience. TinyMCE offers broad flexibility, making it a powerful solution that adapts to a wide range of industries and roles. Its modular design, extensive plugin ecosystem, and seamless integration capabilities allow you to tailor the editor to meet diverse needs—from simple websites to complex enterprise applications—emphasizing its adaptability and design freedom.",
